Process called "create_temp_file" that takes prefix as String and suffix as String returns String:
    Return path of created temporary file with prefix and suffix

Process called "create_temp_directory" that takes prefix as String returns String:
    Return path of created temporary directory with prefix

Process called "get_environment_variable" that takes name as String returns String:
    Return environment variable with name

